Package MessageObjects

Class MessageBody

java.lang.Object
MessageObjects.MessageBody
public class MessageBody
extends java.lang.Object
class MessageBody This class defines all relevant message attributes (except sup. messageType) of all messages provided according to the protocol. Further description of certain message attributes can be found in Message-implementing classes.
